		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Default [2.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Anonymous&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>Ok let me give those of you with a little clue the real CLUE, on gaining level 9 quickly.<br>---<br>first of all what is quickly to you?<br>6 hours? 4 hours? I have done it in 54 minutes!<br>thats right 54 minutes! <br>--- <br>now first of all I DO NOT ENDORSE THIS!<br>because it leaves your skills in the dust however as mentioned in other posts there are ways around this. <br>---<br>A druid that wishes to level in lew of anything else to the exalted lvl of 9 should start in rivervale or if your a woodelf get your rear there as soon as possible. like 24 min after you login, which makes it a 78 min level 9 exp.<br>---<br>There are several quests in rivervale but the one we are concerned with is the Turnip quest! <br>---<br>at first level you get skin like wood and minor healing, start doing the turnip quest go to Darin Leafsway and say "I will take the turnip" then run to the otherside of town across from the bank you will find walla! deputy Eigon, give him the turnips recieve exp and up to 3 sp, after 10 time, go by the burn spell.&nbsp;&nbsp;now scribe it memorize it.<br>---<br>if your a halfling your bound outside if not get bound in town.<br>---<br>go target darin leafsway and cast your burn, VECTOR yourself towards Eigon throught the main square! you may or may not reach him the first time :)<br>---<br>do it till you get darin standing right next to Eigon.  then change your view and setup hot keys, you will need to hail darin every 3 minutes to keep her there, but you can hand the turnips as you get them to deputy Eigon after 50-55 minutes you will be level 9 with out problems! ( I actually went outat 5th and practiced some with 1 h b for 10 minutes)<br>---<br>goodluck</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
